{"tid":2113489,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙田警署廚師疑中招","createTime":"2020-07-18T07:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T07:15:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc28ae96a9d44714390d7be18c58d26ec68e2524","tid":2113489,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200718/7KLODFYI3VJDQLDQVOKJG3JZM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200718%2F7KLODFYI3VJDQLDQVOKJG3JZM4%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTibyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=e424727d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200718%2F7KLODFYI3VJDQLDQVOKJG3JZM4%2F&h=085f667f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200718/7KLODFYI3VJDQLDQVOKJG3JZM4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n沙田警署廚師疑中招<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7-8GGurLTtHpzD_9IA6Fh8acZeU=/1088x725/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KGSBKRQW2T46RIN5QZ7JQQMLWI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7-8GGurLTtHpzD_9IA6Fh8acZeU%3D%2F1088x725%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKGSBKRQW2T46RIN5QZ7JQQMLWI.gif&h=8d94b986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田警署。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府禁止食肆晚市堂食，卻容許警署食堂繼續飯敍，為香港武漢肺炎病毒散播徒添危機。沙田警署食堂一名廚師近日發燒，須接受深喉唾液測試，該食堂昨起暫停營業。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：賽馬會朗逸居院友 職員 染疫<br />\n<br />\n食堂暫停營業<br />\n<br />\n沙田警署食堂一名45歲廚師近日發燒，懷疑感染武肺，要接受深喉唾液測試。據了解，當區助理指揮官（行政）已下令關閉沙田警署食堂，等候測試結果，同在該食堂工作的兩名人員暫時休假。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，沙田警署一名。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至今已有五名警務人員確診，最近一宗為一名47歲男警，原駐守紅磡警署，去年2月因涉及一宗毒品案，被控藏毒及停職，早前須每日到青山警署報到。警方以各區警察食堂均屬於規例（第599F章）附表1所指的其中一類型處所為由，認為晚市禁堂食限制不適用於各區警察食堂。"}]}